FUNCTION BuildReportData GLOBAL
    # ดำเนินการแล้วเสร็จ (เปลี่ยนหน้ากลับ)
    WAIT 2
    IF Contains(Course, $'''เคส3''', True) THEN
        # Only Case3 - เก็บเลขผ่านรายการจ่ายหน้า FP05/FP25 (ไม่เด้งกลับ)
        UIAutomation.GetElementDetails Element: appmask['Window \'รายการ ชี้แจง: รายละเอียดและการเลือก\'']['Pane Doc No หลังรับฝากรายการ (ไม่เด้งกลับ)'] AttributeName: $'''Own Text''' BringToFront: True AttributeValue=> AttributeValue
        Text.ParseText.RegexParseForFirstOccurrence Text: AttributeValue TextToFind: $'''\\d{12}''' StartingPosition: 0 IgnoreCase: False OccurrencePosition=> Position Match=> Match
    ELSE
        UIAutomation.GetElementDetails Element: appmask['Window \'รายการงาน: ชุดการชำระเงิน\'']['Pane Doc No หลังรับฝากรายการ'] AttributeName: $'''Own Text''' BringToFront: True AttributeValue=> AttributeValue
        Text.ParseText.RegexParseForFirstOccurrence Text: AttributeValue TextToFind: $'''\\d{12}''' StartingPosition: 0 IgnoreCase: False OccurrencePosition=> Position Match=> Match
    END
    /# Build resut for report flow action
Header => [timestamp, หมายเลข lots, หมายเลข ca, เงิน lots, เงิน bill, เลขที่เอกสาร, ประเภทเอกสาร เดิม, ประเภทเอกสาร ใหม่, เหตุผล, เอกสารผ่านรายการ]#/
    DateTime.GetCurrentDateTime.Local DateTimeFormat: DateTime.DateTimeFormat.DateAndTime CurrentDateTime=> TimeStamp
    SET TempResultRow TO [TimeStamp, InputLots, InputCA, InputLotsMoney, InputBillMoney, InputDocNo, PaymentCode, NewPaymentCode, Course, Match]
    Variables.AddRowToDataTable.AppendRowToDataTable DataTable: ResultDataTable RowToAdd: TempResultRow
    SET NewPaymentCode TO $'''\'\''''
    # Fetch API logging user
    Web.InvokeWebService.InvokeWebService Url: $'''http://10.4.5.144/rpa''' Method: Web.Method.Post Accept: $'''application/json''' ContentType: $'''application/json''' CustomHeaders: $'''Authorization: Bearer iyqgxrdC6tDgmt5SPYpEIFAo9BbXSaeM918i8f03fORoOcyQhDiTVE8jd46YvJT1''' RequestBody: $'''{
\"flowname\": \"slcs clear lot\",
\"business\": %BA1%,
\"username\": %Username%
}''' ConnectionTimeout: 30 FollowRedirection: True ClearCookies: False FailOnErrorStatus: False EncodeRequestBody: False UserAgent: $'''Mozilla/5.0 (Windows; U; Windows NT 5.1; en-US; rv:1.8.1.21) Gecko/20100312 Firefox/3.6''' Encoding: Web.Encoding.AutoDetect AcceptUntrustedCertificates: False ResponseHeaders=> WebServiceResponseHeaders Response=> WebServiceResponse StatusCode=> StatusCode
END FUNCTION

FUNCTION 'T-Code3_FP05_FP25' GLOBAL
    # T-Code : FP05  (เข้าถึงหน้าการเริ่มต้นเคลียร์ Lots)
    UIAutomation.FocusWindow.FocusByTitleClass Title: $'''SAP Easy Access  PEA''' Class: $''''''
    ON ERROR

    END
    MouseAndKeyboard.SendKeys.FocusAndSendKeys TextToSend: $'''{Control}({N})''' DelayBetweenKeystrokes: 10 SendTextAsHardwareKeys: False
    WAIT (UIAutomation.WaitForWindow.ToOpenByTitleClass Title: $'''SAP Easy Access  PEA''' Class: $'''''' FocusWindow: True) FOR 5 
    ON ERROR

    END
    IF Contains(InputLots, $'''B''', False) THEN
        SET Tcode3 TO $'''FP25'''
    END
    MouseAndKeyboard.SendKeys.FocusAndSendKeys TextToSend: $'''{Control}({Oem2})%Tcode3%{Return}''' DelayBetweenKeystrokes: 100 SendTextAsHardwareKeys: False
    WAIT (UIAutomation.WaitForWindow.ToOpenByTitleClass Title: $'''ชุดการชำระเงิน: จอภาพเริ่มต้น''' Class: $'''''' FocusWindow: True) FOR 15 
    ON ERROR

    END
    Clipboard.SetText Text: InputLots
    MouseAndKeyboard.SendKeys.FocusAndSendKeys TextToSend: $'''{Control}({A}){Control}({V}){Shift}({F7})''' DelayBetweenKeystrokes: 10 SendTextAsHardwareKeys: False
    WAIT (UIAutomation.WaitForWindow.ToOpenByTitleClass Title: $'''รายการงาน: ชุดการชำระเงิน''' Class: $'''''' FocusWindow: True) FOR 5 
    ON ERROR

    END
    # Data not found in FP05
    IF (UIAutomation.IfWindowContains.WindowContainsElement Element: appmask['Window \'ชุดการชำระเงิน: จอภาพเริ่มต้น\'']['Pane ไม่มีข้อมูลใน lots']) THEN
        SET IsDataNotFound TO 1
        Display.ShowMessageDialog.ShowMessageWithTimeout Title: $'''Status''' Message: $'''ไม่พบข้อมูลใน Lost ดำเนินการรายการต่อไป''' Icon: Display.Icon.None Buttons: Display.Buttons.OK DefaultButton: Display.DefaultButton.Button1 IsTopMost: True Timeout: 2
        /# Build resut for report flow action
Header => [timestamp, หมายเลข lots, หมายเลข ca, เงิน lots, เงิน bill, เลขที่เอกสาร, ประเภทเอกสาร เดิม, ประเภทเอกสาร ใหม่, เหตุผล, เอกสารผ่านรายการ]#/
        DateTime.GetCurrentDateTime.Local DateTimeFormat: DateTime.DateTimeFormat.DateAndTime CurrentDateTime=> TimeStamp
        SET TempResultRow TO [TimeStamp, InputLots, InputCA, InputLotsMoney, '-', '-', PaymentCode, '-', 'ไม่พบข้อมูลใน Lots', '-']
        Variables.AddRowToDataTable.AppendRowToDataTable DataTable: ResultDataTable RowToAdd: TempResultRow
        EXIT FUNCTION
    END
    MouseAndKeyboard.SendKeys.FocusAndSendKeys TextToSend: $'''{Control}({Shift}{F2})''' DelayBetweenKeystrokes: 10 SendTextAsHardwareKeys: False
    WAIT (UIAutomation.WaitForWindow.ToOpenByTitleClass Title: $'''กำหนดเกณฑ์ฟิลเตอร์''' Class: $'''''' FocusWindow: True) FOR 15 
    ON ERROR

    END
    MouseAndKeyboard.SendKeys.FocusAndSendKeys TextToSend: $'''{Tab:7}{Down:7}{F7}''' DelayBetweenKeystrokes: 10 SendTextAsHardwareKeys: False
    WAIT 1
    MouseAndKeyboard.SendKeys.FocusAndSendKeys TextToSend: $'''{Tab:2}{Down:4}{F7}''' DelayBetweenKeystrokes: 10 SendTextAsHardwareKeys: False
    WAIT 1
    MouseAndKeyboard.SendKeys.FocusAndSendKeys TextToSend: $'''{Shift}({Tab:3}){Return}''' DelayBetweenKeystrokes: 10 SendTextAsHardwareKeys: False
    WAIT (UIAutomation.WaitForWindow.ToOpenByTitleClass Title: $'''กำหนดค่าสำหรับเกณฑ์การฟิลเตอร์''' Class: $'''''' FocusWindow: True) FOR 15 
    ON ERROR

    END
    MouseAndKeyboard.SendKeys.FocusAndSendKeys TextToSend: $'''%InputCA%{Tab:5}%InputLotsMoney%{Return}''' DelayBetweenKeystrokes: 10 SendTextAsHardwareKeys: False
    WAIT (UIAutomation.WaitForWindow.ToLoseFocusByTitleClass Title: $'''กำหนดค่าสำหรับเกณฑ์การฟิลเตอร์''' Class: $'''''') FOR 5 
    ON ERROR

    END
    MouseAndKeyboard.SendKeys.FocusAndSendKeys TextToSend: $'''{Control}({Alt}{F2})''' DelayBetweenKeystrokes: 10 SendTextAsHardwareKeys: False
    WAIT 1
    IF (UIAutomation.IfWindowContains.WindowContainsElement Element: appmask['Window \'รายการงาน: ชุดการชำระเงิน\'']['Pane ไม่พบผลการ filter']) THEN
        MouseAndKeyboard.SendKeys.FocusAndSendKeys TextToSend: $'''{F3}''' DelayBetweenKeystrokes: 10 SendTextAsHardwareKeys: False
        WAIT (UIAutomation.WaitForWindow.ToOpenByTitleClass Title: $'''ชุดการชำระเงิน: จอภาพเริ่มต้น''' Class: $'''''' FocusWindow: True) FOR 10 
        ON ERROR

        END
        SET IsDataNotFound TO 1
        EXIT FUNCTION
    END
    WAIT (UIAutomation.WaitForWindow.ToOpenByTitleClass Title: $'''รายการ ชี้แจง: รายละเอียดและการเลือก''' Class: $'''''' FocusWindow: True) FOR 15 
    ON ERROR

    END
    # เริ่มตันเคลียร์ Lots แต่ละเคส หลังจากนี้ไป
END FUNCTION

FUNCTION 'T-Code2_FPL9' GLOBAL
    # T-Code : FPL9  (วนลูปเจาะรายละเอียดแต่ละ CA)
    UIAutomation.FocusWindow.FocusByTitleClass Title: $'''SAP Easy Access  PEA''' Class: $''''''
    ON ERROR

    END
    MouseAndKeyboard.SendKeys.FocusAndSendKeys TextToSend: $'''{Control}({N})''' DelayBetweenKeystrokes: 100 SendTextAsHardwareKeys: False
    WAIT (UIAutomation.WaitForWindow.ToOpenByTitleClass Title: $'''SAP Easy Access  PEA''' Class: $'''''' FocusWindow: True) FOR 5 
    ON ERROR

    END
    MouseAndKeyboard.SendKeys.FocusAndSendKeys TextToSend: $'''{Control}({Oem2})%Tcode2%{Return}''' DelayBetweenKeystrokes: 100 SendTextAsHardwareKeys: False
    WAIT (UIAutomation.WaitForWindow.ToOpenByTitleClass Title: $'''การแสดงบัญชี: InitScrn''' Class: $'''''' FocusWindow: True) FOR 5 
    ON ERROR

    END
    LOOP FOREACH CurrentCA IN ExcelDataByLots
        CALL Clear_Variable
        # อ่านค่าจากตาราง Lots
        SET InputLots TO CurrentCA['ชุดการชำระเงิน']
        SET InputCA TO CurrentCA['ค่าฟิลด์แรกที่ต้องการเลือก']

        ON ERROR

        END
        # กรอก SAP
        MouseAndKeyboard.SendKeys.FocusAndSendKeys TextToSend: $'''{Tab:2}%InputCA%{Return}''' DelayBetweenKeystrokes: 100 SendTextAsHardwareKeys: False
        WAIT (UIAutomation.WaitForWindow.ToOpenByTitleClass Title: $'''การแสดงบัญชี: เบสิกลิสต์''' Class: $'''''' FocusWindow: True) FOR 5 
        ON ERROR

        END
        MouseAndKeyboard.SendKeys.FocusAndSendKeys TextToSend: $'''{Tab}{Left:4}{Space}''' DelayBetweenKeystrokes: 100 SendTextAsHardwareKeys: False
        WAIT (OCR.WaitForTextOnScreen.TextOnScreenToAppearWithWindowsOcr TextToFind: $'''Mtrans''' IsRegex: False WindowsOcrLanguage: OCR.WindowsOcrLanguage.English SearchForTextOn: OCR.SearchTarget.EntireScreen ImageWidthMultiplier: 1 ImageHeightMultiplier: 1) FOR 5 
        ON ERROR

        END
        MouseAndKeyboard.SendKeys.FocusAndSendKeys TextToSend: $'''{Tab}{Left:4}{Space}{Tab}{Shift}({Tab:19}){Space}{Down}{Return}''' DelayBetweenKeystrokes: 200 SendTextAsHardwareKeys: False
        # Export Bill
        SET IsBypassXXL TO 1
        CALL Export_XXL
        SET ExcelDataByCA TO TempExcelData
        # Check Case 1-4
        CALL CheckCase_CA
        UIAutomation.FocusWindow.FocusByTitleClass Title: $'''การแสดงบัญชี: เบสิกลิสต์''' Class: $''''''
        ON ERROR

        END
        MouseAndKeyboard.SendKeys.FocusAndSendKeys TextToSend: $'''{F3}''' DelayBetweenKeystrokes: 10 SendTextAsHardwareKeys: False
        WAIT (UIAutomation.WaitForWindow.ToOpenByTitleClass Title: $'''การแสดงบัญชี: InitScrn''' Class: $'''''' FocusWindow: True) FOR 5 
        ON ERROR

        END
    END
    # SAP - Go home
    UIAutomation.FocusWindow.FocusByTitleClass Title: $'''การแสดงบัญชี: InitScrn''' Class: $''''''
    ON ERROR

    END
    UIAutomation.CloseWindow.CloseByTitleClass Title: $'''การแสดงบัญชี: InitScrn''' Class: $''''''
END FUNCTION

    WAIT (UIAutomation.WaitForWindow.ToOpenByTitleClass Title: $'''SAP Easy Access  PEA''' Class: $'''''' FocusWindow: True) FOR 5

FUNCTION SAP_Login GLOBAL
    IF (UIAutomation.IfWindow.IsOpenByTitleClass Title: $'''SAP Easy Access  PEA''' Class: $'''''') THEN
        GOTO IsSapHome
    END
    System.RunApplication.RunApplication ApplicationPath: $'''\"C:\\Program Files (x86)\\SAP\\FrontEnd\\SAPgui\\saplogon.exe\"''' WindowStyle: System.ProcessWindowStyle.Normal ProcessId=> SapProcessId
    LABEL LoginSap
    Variables.IncreaseVariable Value: CountLoginSAP IncrementValue: 1
    IF CountLoginSAP = LoginSapLimit THEN
        Display.ShowMessageDialog.ShowMessageWithTimeout Title: $'''Status''' Message: $'''Login SAP ไม่สำเร็จ (เกิน Limit %LoginSapLimit% ครั้ง)''' Icon: Display.Icon.None Buttons: Display.Buttons.OK DefaultButton: Display.DefaultButton.Button1 IsTopMost: True Timeout: 3
        EXIT Code: 0
    END
    WAIT (UIAutomation.WaitForWindow.ToOpenByTitleClass Title: $'''SAP Logon 750''' Class: $'''''' FocusWindow: True) FOR 5 
    ON ERROR

    END
    LOOP FOREACH CurrentSapUser IN SapUserTable
        MouseAndKeyboard.SendKeys.FocusAndSendKeysByTitleClass Title: $'''SAP Logon 750''' Class: $'''''' TextToSend: $'''{Alt}({L})''' DelayBetweenKeystrokes: 100 SendTextAsHardwareKeys: False
        WAIT (UIAutomation.WaitForWindow.ToOpenByTitleClass Title: $'''SAP''' Class: $'''''' FocusWindow: True) FOR 5 
        ON ERROR

        END
        UIAutomation.SetWindowState.SetStateByTitleClass Title: $'''SAP''' Class: $'''''' State: UIAutomation.WindowState.Maximized
        MouseAndKeyboard.SendKeys.FocusAndSendKeys TextToSend: $'''%CurrentSapUser['Username']%{Tab}''' DelayBetweenKeystrokes: 100 SendTextAsHardwareKeys: False
        MouseAndKeyboard.SendKeys.FocusAndSendKeys TextToSend: $'''%CurrentSapUser['Password']%{Tab}TH{Return}''' DelayBetweenKeystrokes: 100 SendTextAsHardwareKeys: False
        IF (UIAutomation.IfWindow.IsOpenByTitleClass Title: $'''ข้อมูลใบอนุญาตสำหรับการเข้าสู่ระบบแบบผู้ใช้หลายราย''' Class: $'''''') THEN
            MouseAndKeyboard.SendKeys.FocusAndSendKeys TextToSend: $'''{Return}''' DelayBetweenKeystrokes: 100 SendTextAsHardwareKeys: False
            UIAutomation.FocusWindow.FocusByTitleClass Title: $'''SAP Logon 750''' Class: $''''''
            NEXT LOOP
        END
        WAIT (UIAutomation.WaitForWindow.ToOpenByTitleClass Title: $'''SAP Easy Access  PEA''' Class: $'''''' FocusWindow: True) FOR 3 
        ON ERROR

        END
        IF (UIAutomation.IfWindow.IsFocusedByTitleClass Title: $'''SAP Easy Access  PEA''' Class: $'''''') THEN
            GOTO IsSapHome
        END
    END
    IF (UIAutomation.IfWindow.IsNotOpenByTitleClass Title: $'''SAP Easy Access  PEA''' Class: $'''''') THEN
        GOTO LoginSap
    END
    MouseAndKeyboard.SendKeys.FocusAndSendKeys TextToSend: $'''{Return}{F12}{Return}{F12}''' DelayBetweenKeystrokes: 1000 SendTextAsHardwareKeys: False
    LABEL IsSapHome
    WAIT (UIAutomation.WaitForWindow.ToOpenByTitleClass Title: $'''SAP Easy Access  PEA''' Class: $'''''' FocusWindow: True) FOR 10
    UIAutomation.SetWindowState.SetStateByTitleClass Title: $'''SAP Easy Access  PEA''' Class: $'''''' State: UIAutomation.WindowState.Maximized
    MouseAndKeyboard.SendKeys.FocusAndSendKeys TextToSend: $'''{Control}({Oem2})''' DelayBetweenKeystrokes: 10 SendTextAsHardwareKeys: False
END FUNCTION

label: CheckCase_CA
content:
FUNCTION CheckCase_CA GLOBAL
    # 1. Prepare Filtered Data
    Variables.FilterDataTable DataTable: ExcelDataByCA FilterParameters: { ^['RULE', 'COLUMN', 'OPERATOR', 'VALUE'], [$'''Or''', $'''สัญญาณสี''', $'''Contains''', RedRegex], [$'''Or''', $'''สัญญาณสี''', $'''Contains''', YellowRegex] } FilteredDataTable=> FilteredOnlyYellowRed
    IF FilteredOnlyYellowRed.RowsCount <> 0 THEN
        Variables.FilterDataTable DataTable: FilteredOnlyYellowRed FilterParameters: { ^['RULE', 'COLUMN', 'OPERATOR', 'VALUE'], [$'''And''', $'''จำนวนเงิน''', $'''GreaterThanOrEqual''', InputLotsMoney - 0.12], [$'''And''', $'''จำนวนเงิน''', $'''LessThanOrEqual''', InputLotsMoney + 0.12] } FilteredDataTable=> FilteredCase2_LotsEqualBill
    END
    # 2. Open and key CA and Lots money in FP05  or  Bypass when no data in lots
    CALL 'T-Code3_FP05_FP25'
    IF IsDataNotFound = 1 THEN
        GOTO 'End from main Tcode3 (FP05)'
    END
    # 3.1 Run Check Case1 - All Green
    IF FilteredOnlyYellowRed.RowsCount = 0 THEN
        CALL Do_Case1_เงินรับฝาก
        SET InputLotsMoney TO 0
    END
    # 3.2 Run Check Case2 - Lots = Bill
    IF FilteredCase2_LotsEqualBill.RowsCount = 1 THEN
        SET InputDocNo TO FilteredCase2_LotsEqualBill[0]['เลขที่เอกสาร']
        CALL Do_Case2_ผ่านรายการออนไลน์
        SET InputLotsMoney TO 0
        GOTO 'End Check Lots = 0'
    END
    # Run Case 3 & 4
    IF FilteredOnlyYellowRed.RowsCount > 0 THEN
        LOOP FOREACH CurrentYellowRed IN FilteredOnlyYellowRed
            SET InputDocNo TO CurrentYellowRed['เลขที่เอกสาร']
            SET InputBillMoney TO CurrentYellowRed['จำนวนเงิน']
            IF InputLotsMoney > InputBillMoney THEN
                # Run Case3 - Lots > Bill
                CALL 'Do_Case3_ผ่านรายการออนไลน์ Ptl'
                Variables.DecreaseVariable Value: InputLotsMoney DecrementValue: InputBillMoney
            ELSE
                # Run Case4 - Lots < Bill
                CALL Do_Case4_ตัดชำระบางส่วน
                Variables.DecreaseVariable Value: InputLotsMoney DecrementValue: InputBillMoney
            END
            IF InputLotsMoney <= 0 THEN
                GOTO 'End Check Lots = 0'
            END
        END
    END
    IF InputLotsMoney > 0 THEN
        CALL Do_Case1_เงินรับฝาก
    END
    LABEL 'End Check Lots = 0'
    # ทำทุกเคสเสร็จถอยออกจาก T-Code3 : FP05
    WAIT (UIAutomation.WaitForWindow.ToOpenByTitleClass Title: $'''รายการงาน: ชุดการชำระเงิน''' Class: $'''''' FocusWindow: True) FOR 5 
    ON ERROR

    END
    MouseAndKeyboard.SendKeys.FocusAndSendKeys TextToSend: $'''{F3}''' DelayBetweenKeystrokes: 10 SendTextAsHardwareKeys: False
    LABEL 'End from main Tcode3 (FP05)'
    WAIT (UIAutomation.WaitForWindow.ToOpenByTitleClass Title: $'''ชุดการชำระเงิน: จอภาพเริ่มต้น''' Class: $'''''' FocusWindow: True) FOR 15 
    ON ERROR

    END
    UIAutomation.CloseWindow.CloseByTitleClass Title: $'''ชุดการชำระเงิน: จอภาพเริ่มต้น''' Class: $''''''
END FUNCTION

FUNCTION Variables GLOBAL
    # SAP Config
    Variables.CreateNewDatatable InputTable: { ^['Username', 'Password'], [$'''s3aedaa02''', $'''10317*'''] } DataTable=> SapUserTable
    SET BA1 TO $'''L021'''
    SET StartDate TO $'''01.01.2024'''
    SET Tcode1 TO $'''ZCACR028'''
    SET Tcode2 TO $'''FPL9'''
    SET Tcode3 TO $'''FP05'''
    SET Company TO 9000
    SET BA2 TO $'''*
'''
    SET CountLoginSAP TO 0
    SET LoginSapLimit TO 10
    # Check Case Config
    SET GreenRegex TO $'''@08'''
    SET RedRegex TO $'''@0A'''
    SET YellowRegex TO $'''@09'''
    SET InputLotsMoney TO 0
    SET IsBypassXXL TO 0
    SET IsDataNotFound TO 0
    # Path Config
    System.GetEnvironmentVariable.GetEnvironmentVariable Name: $'''USERNAME''' Value=> Username
    Folder.GetSpecialFolder SpecialFolder: Folder.SpecialFolder.DesktopDirectory SpecialFolderPath=> DesktopPath
    Folder.Create FolderPath: DesktopPath FolderName: $'''RPA_Results''' Folder=> RpaResultPath
    DateTime.GetCurrentDateTime.Local DateTimeFormat: DateTime.DateTimeFormat.DateAndTime CurrentDateTime=> CurrentDateTime
    Text.ConvertDateTimeToText.FromCustomDateTime DateTime: CurrentDateTime CustomFormat: $'''dd-MM-yyyy''' Result=> FormattedDate
    Text.ConvertDateTimeToText.FromCustomDateTime DateTime: CurrentDateTime CustomFormat: $'''HH.mm.ss''' Result=> FormattedTime
    Folder.Create FolderPath: RpaResultPath FolderName: FormattedDate Folder=> RpaResultPath
    Folder.Create FolderPath: RpaResultPath FolderName: BA1 Folder=> RpaResultPath

FUNCTION Main_copy GLOBAL
    # 0. Flow Version
    SET Version TO $'''1.0.1'''
    # 1. ประกาศตัวแปร
    CALL Variables
    # 2. เปืดโปรแกรม SAP
    CALL SAP_Login
    # 3. จัดการการออกรายงาน Lots
    IF (File.IfFile.Exists File: ReportFilePath) THEN
        # Load exist file ZCACR028 report for current day
        Excel.LaunchExcel.LaunchAndOpenUnderExistingProcess Path: ReportFilePath Visible: True ReadOnly: False Instance=> TempExcelInstance
        Excel.ReadFromExcel.ReadAllCells Instance: TempExcelInstance ReadAsText: False FirstLineIsHeader: True RangeValue=> ExcelDataByLots
        Excel.CloseExcel.Close Instance: TempExcelInstance
        SET IsBypassXXL TO 1
    ELSE
        CALL 'T-Code1_ZCACR028'
    END
    IF IsDataNotFound = 1 THEN
        GOTO 'Gen Result Report'
    END
    # 4. ดำเนินการแก้ไข Lots แต่ละ CA
    CALL 'T-Code2_FPL9'
    # 5. ออกรายงานสรุป Result ของ RPA flow
    LABEL 'Gen Result Report'
    IF ResultDataTable.RowsCount > 0 THEN
        Excel.LaunchExcel.LaunchUnderExistingProcess Visible: True Instance=> TempExcelInstance
        Excel.WriteToExcel.WriteNamedCell Instance: TempExcelInstance Value: ResultDataTable CellName: $'''A1''' WriteToAllCells: False
        Excel.WriteToExcel.WriteNamedCell Instance: TempExcelInstance Value: ResultDataTable.ColumnHeadersRow CellName: $'''A1''' WriteToAllCells: False
        Excel.CloseExcel.CloseAndSaveAs Instance: TempExcelInstance DocumentFormat: Excel.ExcelFormat.OpenXmlWorkbook DocumentPath: ResultFilePath
    END
    CALL Variables
    System.RunApplication.RunApplicationAndWaitToLoad ApplicationPath: $'''%RpaResultPath%\\''' WindowStyle: System.ProcessWindowStyle.Normal Timeout: 3
ON ERROR

END
    Display.ShowMessageDialog.ShowMessageWithTimeout Title: $'''Status''' Message: $'''จบการทำงาน Finish!!''' Icon: Display.Icon.None Buttons: Display.Buttons.OK DefaultButton: Display.DefaultButton.Button1 IsTopMost: True Timeout: 3
    EXIT Code: 0
END FUNCTION
